{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sidekiq/sidekiq/issues/6764","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sidekiq/sidekiq","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sidekiq/sidekiq/issues/6764/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sidekiq/sidekiq/issues/6764/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sidekiq/sidekiq/issues/6764/events","html_url":"https://github.com/sidekiq/sidekiq/issues/6764","id":3242298743,"node_id":"I_kwDOADDA9M7BQY13","number":6764,"title":"Metrics possibly getting lost if Sidekiq process restarts right after job finished","user":{"login":"monkeyWzr","id":12955546,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEyOTU1NTQ2","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/12955546?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/monkeyWzr","html_url":"https://github.com/monkeyWzr","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/monkeyWzr/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/monkeyWzr/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/monkeyWzr/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/monkeyWzr/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/monkeyWzr/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/monkeyWzr/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/monkeyWzr/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/monkeyWzr/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/monkeyWzr/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2025-07-18T07:59:09Z","updated_at":"2025-07-20T18:13:25Z","closed_at":"2025-07-20T18:13:25Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"Ruby version: 3.4.4\nRails version: 8.0.2\nSidekiq / Pro / Enterprise version(s): sidekiq (8.0.5) / sidekiq-pro (8.0.1) / sidekiq-ent (8.0.1)\n\nHi there @mperham !\n\nI am using `SIDEKIQ_MAXMEM_MB` to have sidekiqswarm automatically restart Sidekiq processes. The restart happens right after a job's execution if memory usage exceeds the threshold. \nMeanwhile, metrics flushing happens on every `:beat` event. \nSo if a job finishes and the process restarts between beats, the metrics for that job aren't collected. \n\nSample code for reproducing without sidekiq-ent:\n```ruby\nclass SomeJob\n  include Sidekiq::Job\n\n  def perform\n    puts \"job performed\"\n    Process.kill(:TERM, Process.pid)\n  end\nend\n```\n\nI'm wondering if it's ok to:\n* flush metrics on `:shutdown` event as well\n* or, fire a `:beat` event during shutdown procedure\n\nI'd be happy to open a pull request for this! \n\nLooking forward to your thoughts üôè ","closed_by":{"login":"mperham","id":2911,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI5MTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2911?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/mperham","html_url":"https://github.com/mperham","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mperham/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mperham/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mperham/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mperham/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mperham/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mperham/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mperham/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mperham/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mperham/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sidekiq/sidekiq/issues/6764/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray